src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n雖然客戶借出股票後不可作沽售或用作認沽期權行使，其他股東權益，例如派息、供股等，仍受全面保障。</blockquote><br />\n收息個手續費邊個比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff8a01a3af0f1fe00ede3ac60ed363ee3b79118","tid":284622,"uid":93245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:45:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁多巴打對個沽空功能有興趣，請先睇睇下面英文寫嘅沽空十戎，投資/投機前先求知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://moneymorning.com/2010/03/15/short-selling/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoneymorning.com%2F2010%2F03%2F15%2Fshort-selling%2F&d=ASA2f9127MnG1Kvz1q%2FNAozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=8b1bb634\" target=\"_blank\">https://moneymorning.com/2010/03/15/short-selling/</a></blockquote>應該無咩人想沽空<br />\n借貨賺息就多</blockquote><br />\n散户話玩熊仔唔好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n借貨俾人沽不嬲大行都做緊<br />\n<br />\n反而想知條queue有冇priority, 一通老散分唔分到餐飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪同平時沽貨一樣，無分別"},{"pid":"7fd06f4a61f6c0c0a658d725f79b4fcbc8fbaeee","tid":284622,"uid":44980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:07:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.blis.gov.hk/blis_ind.nsf/AllVerAllChinDoc/8369A1EDEBEDD9E7482579C700084B37?OpenDocument\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.blis.gov.hk%2Fblis_ind.nsf%2FAllVerAllChinDoc%2F8369A1EDEBEDD9E7482579C700084B37%3FOpenDocument&d=ASA2f9127MnG1Kvz1q%2FNAozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=85cf818a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.blis.gov.hk/blis_ind.nsf/AllVerAllChinDoc/8369A1EDEBEDD9E7482579C700084B37?OpenDocument</a> <br />\n税局條例"},{"pid":"732435b6c013e7afaa80a1fd4fd687aae61d7379","tid":284622,"uid":44980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:32:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>$270係一次性交or年費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n股&nbsp;票&nbsp;借&nbsp;貸&nbsp;及&nbsp;沽&nbsp;空&nbsp;功&nbsp;能&nbsp;常&nbsp;見&nbsp;問&nbsp;題<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;一通自通知客戶下周一開始有股票借貸及沽空服務後，反應熱烈，但大多數一通客戶未曾試過借貨或沽空，所以在此再次向客戶提供更多資訊。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;稅局$270收費<br />\n<br />\n此項收費是一次性，即支付後一世不用再付（除非稅局更改政策）。不過，借入及借出登記是分別要交$270予稅局，即是說，客戶同時開立借入及借出戶口總共要交$540。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會唔會有巴打係一通做睇到我問"},{"pid":"5f64e82aa9fffed640b27de3109dc634ca06b8ef","tid":284622,"uid":82587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:43:16.000Z","msg":"太多人問野要出email<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8569cb6a663bfe7e8ea4555bf01d9b01c13973","tid":284622,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:47:36.000Z","msg":"除了沽空睇跌之外借貨的原因<br />\n<br />\n客戶如果要行使認沽期權或認購期權短倉被行使時沒有持貨，可以立即借貨應付行使，避免被收取無貨沽空罰金。客戶若有此需要，請盡早開立借入戶口，因為開戶在收齊客戶文件後再要去稅局登記。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乜唔係一通借錢幫你開市掃貨咩"},{"pid":"a3b3067630503ebb628ef8868028045f60c07212","tid":284622,"uid":93900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T18:22:27.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"3376826878ef47837731522f82f6cedc3cd27ca8","tid":284622,"uid":635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T18:46:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>買咩最易被借出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁一定係垃圾股最多人沽空，問題係你會唔會買果D股嚟長揸先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋我諗有相關牛熊／窩輪既股票，需求又會相對少左（睇淡可以買put）</blockquote>我諗5、941、700、2628呢d大股</blockquote><br />\n借出股票後並非即時收取利息，必須有客戶借入並獲分配時才會收到利息。當其他一通客戶借入股票時，<strong>首先會以一通本身可借出的股數應付借貨需求</strong>，若總借入股數超過一通本身可借出的股數時，多出的股數便會在晚上約十時以加權平均基準分予借出股票的客戶，即是借出股數越大，獲分配的股數便越多。利息便會按獲分配的股數收市市值以香港上海匯豐銀行的最優惠利率（現時為年利率5厘）計算，並計入現金戶口的累計利息，月尾結算。<br />\n<br />\n大股當然多D成交<br />\n但係我估一通都預左會有多D需求，預備定D股票借俾人（有錯請指正）<br />\n到佢用哂呢個pool既股票，先至會用我地散戶果D借俾人<br />\n變左我地散戶成功借出既機會都未必會高左</blockquote>屌，咁既係垃撚圾<br />\n想自己袋又驚比人loan爆呃小戶儲貨擺佢到<br />\n本身轉d倉入去擺無所謂<br />\n但一年都唔知賺唔賺得返個270</blockquote><br />\n借足一年賺5%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 借出去一皮野借足一年係有500收"},{"pid":"3552f50624436ebac81702a221ce02aac6290fb3","tid":284622,"uid":44980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T04:03:43.000Z","msg":"星期一出但仲未有得申請係乜玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03f3c2571e87f89c041592ceabf9a08f43925df","tid":284622,"uid":54884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T04:47:45.000Z","msg":"有10手長和 一直都係做下SC 如果做SC +借貨俾人沽空 都幾好 但係要俾按金"},{"pid":"9bb08b7997b2801330bd3099ae057ddff00c38f0","tid":284622,"uid":29773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T05:12:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>星期一出但仲未有得申請係乜玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪就係星期一先開始接受申請囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n長玩長有<br />\n駛乜急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過硬係覺得好少人會用沽空功能"},{"pid":"85410ae2c1d36f741011a3366ca4fc950eedec32","tid":284622,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>星期一出但仲未有得申請係乜玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪就係星期一先開始接受申請囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n長玩長有<br />\n駛乜急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過硬係覺得好少人會用沽空功能</blockquote><br />\n大把野沽"},{"pid":"fa18d184911cc38f086d41c685fe3dd391b31690","tid":284622,"uid":7688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T07:06:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>星期一出但仲未有得申請係乜玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"